{"ja392:0.1":"Jataka ","ja392:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja392:0.3":"Kharaputtavagga ","ja392:0.4":"7. Singhapupphajataka ","ja392:1.1":"“Yametam varijam puppham, ","ja392:1.2":"Adinnam upasinghasi; ","ja392:1.3":"Ekangametam theyyanam, ","ja392:1.4":"Gandhathenosi marisa”. ","ja392:2.1":"“Na harami na bhanjami, ","ja392:2.2":"ara singhami varijam; ","ja392:2.3":"Atha kena nu vannena, ","ja392:2.4":"gandhathenoti vuccati. ","ja392:3.1":"Yoyam bhisani khanati, ","ja392:3.2":"pundarikani bhanjati; ","ja392:3.3":"Evam akinnakammanto, ","ja392:3.4":"kasma eso na vuccati”. ","ja392:4.1":"“Akinnaluddo puriso, ","ja392:4.2":"dhaticelamva makkhito; ","ja392:4.3":"Tasmim me vacanam natthi, ","ja392:4.4":"tancarahami vattave. ","ja392:5.1":"Ananganassa posassa, ","ja392:5.2":"niccam sucigavesino; ","ja392:5.3":"Valaggamattam papassa, ","ja392:5.4":"abbhamattamva khayati”. ","ja392:6.1":"“Addha mam yakkha janasi, ","ja392:6.2":"atho mam anukampasi; ","ja392:6.3":"Punapi yakkha vajjasi, ","ja392:6.4":"yada passasi edisam”. ","ja392:7.1":"“Neva tam upajivami, ","ja392:7.2":"napi te bhatakamhase; ","ja392:7.3":"Tvameva bhikkhu janeyya, ","ja392:7.4":"yena gaccheyya suggatin”ti. ","ja392:8.1":"Singhapupphajatakam sattamam. "}